my beau and i decided to do a pizza week pasquarelli s was third on our list choosing from a list of top pizza shops in pgh it is by far the best GOODREVIEW pizza we ve ever had we tried a small white and a med red sauce with stuffed crust priced reasonably well for the unbelievably mouth watering pies they serve take out service only and cash only but even though it s about 30 minutes from where we live we ll certainly be back
